<content type="application/x.deki0805+xml" title="popupset"><body xmlns:eval="http://mindtouch.com/2007/dekiscript">
<div class="noinclude"><span class="script">template.XULRefElem()</span></div>
<p>A container for <span class="script">template.XULElem("menupopup")</span>, <span class="script">template.XULElem("panel")</span> and <span class="script">template.XULElem("tooltip")</span> elements. This element is optional; the given elements need not appear in a popupset container.</p>
<p>More information is available in the <a title="en/XUL_Tutorial/Popup_Menus" href="/en/XUL_Tutorial/Popup_Menus">XUL tutorial</a>.</p>
<h3 name="Examples">Examples</h3>
<div class="float-right"><img src="/@api/deki/files/465/=XUL_ref_popup.png" alt="Image:XUL_ref_popup.png" class="internal" /></div>
<pre>
&lt;popupset&gt;
  &lt;menupopup id="clipmenu"&gt;
    &lt;menuitem label="Cut"/&gt;
    &lt;menuitem label="Copy"/&gt;
    &lt;menuitem label="Paste"/&gt;
  &lt;/menupopup&gt;
&lt;/popupset&gt;
&lt;label value="Right click for popup" context="clipmenu"/&gt;
</pre>
